<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
        <h2 class="h1-responsive font-weight-bold text-center my-1">Recent posts</h2>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-8">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row p-2">
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <div class="view overlay rounded z-depth-2 mb-4">
                            <div class="comment-img-box">
                                <img class="img-fluid" src="https://mdbootstrap.com/img/Photos/Others/img%20(27).jpg" alt="Sample image">
                            </div>
                            <a>
                                <div class="mask rgba-white-slight"></div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-8">
                        <div class="d-flex flex-row align-items-center">
                            <h5 class="font-weight-bold mr-3"><strong>&#64;Model.Title</strong></h5>
                            <a href="#!" class="green-text">
                                <h6 class="font-weight-bold mb-2"><i class="fas fa-utensils pr-2"></i>&#64;Model.Category</h6>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-wrap">Nam libero tempore, cum soluta nobis est eligendi optio cumque nihil impedit quo minus id quod maxime placeat facere possimus, omnis voluptas assumenda est, omnis dolor repellendus et aut officiis debitis.
                        </p>
                        <p>by <a href="#"><strong>&#64;Model.Creator.Name</strong></a>, &#64;Model.CreatedAt</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer rgba-white-strong">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 card-header d-flex flex-row justify-content-between align-items-middle rgba-white-strong border-0">
                        <h4>Comments</h4>
                        <small class="text-muted">*Must user different method to pass comments on posts to template</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-11 offset-1">
                        <div class="media">
                            <img class="d-flex rounded-circle avatar z-depth-1-half mr-3" src="https://mdbootstrap.com/img/Photos/Avatars/avatar-5.jpg" alt="Avatar">
                            <div class="media-body">
                                <h5 class="mt-0 font-weight-bold blue-text">Anna Smith</h5>
                                <p>
                                    <small>
                                        Cras sit amet nibh libero, in gravida nulla. Nulla vel metus scelerisque ante sollicitudin. Cras purus
                                        odio, vestibulum in vulputate at, tempus viverra turpis. Fusce condimentum nunc ac nisi vulputate
                                        fringilla. Donec lacinia congue felis in faucibus.
                                    </small>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md-form input-group mb-3 mx-0 px-0">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Post a comment" aria-label="Post a comment" aria-describedby="comment-button">
                            <div class="input-group-append">
                                <button class="btn btn-md btn-secondary m-0" type="button" id="comment-button">Post</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="header pt-3 blue-gradient">
                <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <h5 class="white-text mb-3 pt-3 font-weight-bold">Posts Help</h5>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="mb-md-0 mb-5">
                    The posts page can be used for more than just posts and is optional. Apply what you need to the page and place it in the correct Views folder.
                    Other ways to use this page is displaying articles and peoples thoughts on them, something like twitter where users can post whatever (within appropriate guidelines) and other users can comment on posts, etc. One thing that must be considered is using different models for a single page. <a href="https://www.c-sharpcorner.com/UploadFile/ff2f08/multiple-models-in-single-view-in-mvc/" target="_blank">Here</a> is a resource on using multiple models within one view.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
